The paper deals with the estimation of a random process in a radar scenario, which involves signal processing and statistical inference. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves sampling theory, which falls under cs.SI (Signal Processing). The scattering function is a concept from signal processing, which suggests cs.SP (Signal Processing) as another likely category. The paper also involves analysis and estimation of the random process, which falls under cs.MM (Mathematical Methods). Finally, the paper involves numerical methods for estimation, which suggests cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) as a possible category.
